From: CTS Exam Bug Injection
Subject: [PATCH] DisplayInfo.equals() rotation 比較遺漏

此 patch 移除 DisplayInfo.equals() 中對 rotation 欄位的比較，
導致旋轉變化時無法正確觸發 onDisplayChanged 回調。

涉及檔案：
- DisplayInfo.java: equals() 方法遺漏 rotation 比較
- DisplayManagerGlobal.java: 使用 equals() 決定是否發送回調  
- LogicalDisplay.java: 從 WindowManager 接收 rotation 更新

---
 .../java/android/view/DisplayInfo.java        | 3 +--
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/core/java/android/view/DisplayInfo.java b/core/java/android/view/DisplayInfo.java
index abcd1234..efgh5678 100644
--- a/core/java/android/view/DisplayInfo.java
+++ b/core/java/android/view/DisplayInfo.java
@@ -423,8 +423,7 @@ public final class DisplayInfo implements Parcelable {
                 && logicalWidth == other.logicalWidth
                 && logicalHeight == other.logicalHeight
                 && Objects.equals(displayCutout, other.displayCutout)
-                && rotation == other.rotation
-                && modeId == other.modeId
+                && modeId == other.modeId
                 && renderFrameRate == other.renderFrameRate
                 && defaultModeId == other.defaultModeId
                 && userPreferredModeId == other.userPreferredModeId
